column5: Hello all, went out this morning for a bit in Mississauga. The water's naturally high and murky. I was using a egg-suckin' leech trying to get it the bottom. Had one nice hit, got cold..I'm really concerned about taking an unitentional dive into the river, so I didn't stay to long.  The sun was out, blue skies and several fishers there, but I never saw a 'bow landed.  Tight lines all!
